title: 462.364 INCONSISTENT LAWS.
text: Inconsistent special laws and general laws of special application are superseded by sections 462.351 to 462.364 to the extent of inconsistency. Nothing in sections 462.351 to 462.364 is to be construed to affect, alter or modify the provisions of Special Laws of 1887, chapter 108, or Laws 1933, chapter 93.
